title: Couple With Heart Person Person No Skin Tone Medium Light Skin Tone
description: Represents a ropersontic couple composed of two women, one with a medium-light skin tone. It signifies love, partnership, and affection between two women.
apple_vendor_description: This heartwarming emoji on Apple devices depicts a couple united by a prominent, softly rendered heart, with one figure in a medium-light skin tone. Apple's design language imbues the figures with smooth gradients and gentle curves, creating a sense of tender connection and shared affection. The overall aesthetic, with its realistic lighting, suggests a celebration of love, partnership, and the beautiful diversity of relationships.
